Name: checkmark

Type: property

Syntax: set the checkmark of <menuItem> to {true | false}

Summary: Has no effect and is included in <LiveCode> for compatibility with imported <HyperCard> <stacks>.

Introduced: 1.0

OS: ios,android

Platforms: desktop,server,web,mobile

Description:
In HyperCard, the <checkmark> <property> determines whether a <menu item> has a checkmark next to it.

A handler can set the <checkmark> to any <value> without causing a <error|script error>, but the actual checkmark is not changed.

